title: Government Purchases of Goods and Services, State and Local Government for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1946 (2)--Original Data, 1946-1967. Unadjusted Figures Have Been Multiplied By 4 To Derive Totals At Annual Rate. Source: U.S. Department Of Commerce, For 1939-1945 Data: National Income, 1954 Edition, A Supplement To The Survey Of Current Business; For 1946: August 1966 Supplement To Survey Of Current Business And Subsequent Monthly Issues
